OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,GThe impending 70th anniversary of
OL,7,Gcommercial television is being marked
OL,8,Gby ITV's regional news programmes.
OL,10,FThe irony seems to be lost.
OL,12,FTo the TV historian, the fact the
OL,13,Foccasion is being marked in this way
OL,14,Fhighlights how modern ITV has little
OL,15,Fin common with the old regional
OL,16,Ffederation.
OL,18,FOf course, it is absolutely right that
OL,19,Fthe 70th anniversary of Independent
OL,20,FTelevision should be marked. There is
OL,21,Fmuch to celebrate
