OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,FIt is just about possible to argue
OL,7,Fthat ITV plc goes back to 1955.
OL,9,FBy a tortuous route, the heritage of
OL,10,FATV is now the property of ITV plc.
OL,12,FFor many years Central was cut off
OL,13,Ffrom its original parent after ACC
OL,14,F(which owned ATV) sold its stake in
OL,15,Fthe company, depriving it of the vast
OL,16,Fmajority of material made before 1982.
OL,18,FHowever the original London weekday
OL,19,Fcompany Associated Rediffusion and its
OL,20,Fchild Thames have long gone.
