OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,FGranada TV ` the oldest company
OL,7,Fdirectly represented in ITV plc `
OL,8,Fstarted in 1956.
OL,10,FMore importantly, It seems bizarre for
OL,11,Fregional programmes to be marking this
OL,12,Fanniversary ` surely this anniversary
OL,13,Fshould only be properly marked in
OL,14,Fnetwork output?
OL,16,FITV Cymru Wales had an interesting
OL,17,Fitem looking back to the original
OL,18,Fcompany for Wales and the West TWW.
