OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,FWhen the original local franchisee
OL,7,Fwent on the air it was a big deal `
OL,8,Fnot merely the extension of an
OL,9,Fexisting broadcaster.
OL,11,FNone of this is a criticism of the
OL,12,Fregional news items themselves, some
OL,13,Fof which have been excellent.
OL,15,FIt just seems strange to intertwine
OL,16,Fwhat were once proud, distinct regions
OL,17,Fwith their own history and heritage
OL,18,Fwith the big national anniversary in
OL,19,Fthis way.
OL,21,FIt will all look strange should local
OL,22,Fanniversaries merit attention too.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
