OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,FWill UTV be caught up in the current
OL,7,F70th birthday nostalgia? It'll be odd
OL,8,Fif this happens given how often
OL,9,Fviewers have been reminded over the
OL,10,Fyears of its opening night on 31st
OL,11,FOctober 1959.
OL,13,FThen again. so much water has passed
OL,14,Funder the bridge since ITV plc came
OL,15,Finto being in 2004.
OL,17,FThis week ITV News London included a
OL,18,Fwell-made report on the demolition of
OL,19,FLWT's iconic south bank studios.
