OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,FI will avoid, however, referring to
OL,7,Fthem as the London Television Centre
OL,8,Ffor obvious reasons to all of us of a
OL,9,Fcertain age. As far as I am concerned
OL,10,Fthere was only one Television Centre
OL,11,Fin London. LWT's home was the South
OL,12,FBank.
OL,14,FWhat reminds us of the passage of the
OL,15,Ftime is that the reporter, rightly,
OL,16,Fexplained just what London Weekend
OL,17,FTelevision was.
OL,19,FHe had to. Why would anybody below 30
OL,20,Fknow about the way ITV in London used
OL,21,Fto work? And many more would simply
OL,22,Fhave forgotten.
