OL,3,C70th anniversary of ITV being
OL,4,Ccelebrated on regional news programmes
OL,6,FBut back to the 70th birthday bash.
OL,8,FMany of the regional pieces have told
OL,9,Fthe local story well, underlying just
OL,10,Fwhy marking the occasion in regional
OL,11,Fnews programmes is confusing.
OL,13,FIf ITV wants to celebrate its
OL,14,Fheritage, please emphasise that the
OL,15,Fstory is about entirely separate and
OL,16,Fproud companies. Some of them, but not
OL,17,Fall, have their legacies in the
OL,18,Fbroadcaster of today.
